version_description: I tried to match the character of the original with some acoustic chords. It's in the same key as the original without capo. The recurring theme on the high E string (3rd to 2nd fret) can easily be played simultaneously to the other chords. The bridge part as well as the outro is still missing. The Dm in the chorus can also be played as a major D, depending on personal taste.
Young Modern by Silverchair full album chords. It's 99% accurate and a joy to experience. Various capo changes but all standard tuning. TURN IT UP.
